<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HOME PAGE</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #222;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: #2a4365;
        }
        hr {
            border: none;
            border-top: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            margin: 1.5rem auto;
            width: 80%;
        }
        p {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        span {
            color: #3182ce;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        div, form {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        button {
            background: #3182ce;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s;
            font-weight: 500;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(49,130,206,0.08);
        }
        button:hover {
            background: #265a8f;
        }
        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #2d3748;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }
            p, h2 {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            button {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 0.75rem 0;
            }
            hr {
                width: 95%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>
        Welcome to DataVerse: Your Gateway to the Ultimate Company Database!
    </h1>
    <hr>
    <p>
        Unlock the power of data. Connect, explore, and manage your users with ease.<br>
        <span>Fast. Secure. Reliable.</span>
    </p>
    <div>
        <form action="/users" method="GET">
            <button type="submit"></button>
                Access User Data
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <h2>the total no. of user are:<%= count %></h2>
    <form action="/user/new">
  <button type="submit">Join Us Today</button>
</form>

</body>
</html>